description.en:
Kianite is a community governed DeFi protocol ecosystem. The goal of Kianite is to create a suite of DeFi products that vertically integrate with each other to maximise returns for users.

Our flagship product on Kianite is to create community governed indices where community members will use the Kianite governance token to vote on different aspects of the index. Such as composition: the tokens that go into the index, weighting: the percentage that each token holds in the portfolio, the market cap min or max requirement of the token to be added to the index and more.

We will also have a DEX product and lending product that will be built around the index product to add more engagement and utility to the indices.
